  "answer": "A) Clinical flap monitoring continues after successful restoration of arterial inflow and venous outflow. The mainstay of postoperative free flap monitoring is clinical assessment (see Table 45-2), although supplementary instrument monitoring also can be helpful. (See Schwartz 9th ed., p 1657.)",
